      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BELLA SUPREME (5) scored a most impressive win two back then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 5.5 lengths 4th at this track (22.75). Better than last start and worth following up. HENRY BALE (4) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (22.78) at this track behind Mermaid Lady in a Bottom Up - Grade 5. Chased the leaders and with a clean run can be prominent. Can feature again. RUBY'S SHOW (8) was below best at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth at this track, but was among the placings at Geelong three back. Well placed here and should do much better. SLEEK MONIQUE (2) will give backers a sight.",
